short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play Robo Recycle Rush directly from your Chrome browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Robo Recycle Rush drops you into an engaging 2D platformer, where you take the role of a purpose-driven robot with a crucial task: cleaning up trash. With humanity conspicuously absent, your mission remains clear: use a range of dynamic maneuvers such as wall jump and dash to swiftly gather garbage . Collecting as much rubbish as possible before your battery life runs out. Utilize our cutting-edge kinetic-to-mechanical energy technology for peak efficiency.  When your battery runs low, you'll be recharged and relaunched to continue your crucial task. 

Let's clean up this world, one piece of trash at a time!

Its recommended to at least get to level 10 to experience as much as possible
